mendments.</s><s>Moderately halophilic or halotolerant.</s><s>Some species are alkaliphilic or alkalitolerant.</s><s>Peptidoglycan is of the A4<em>α</em> type, l-lys–gly–l-Glu, l-lys–l-glu or lys–gly–d-Asp.</s><s>The G+C content of the DNA is 64–72 mol%.</s></p></content></protolog>